currently only a JIRA Administrator can modify the list of selection parameters available for a custom field. project managers need to be able to modify the values for project-specific custom fields the same way they can modify the list of versions and components.

My apologies if this is a duplicate - I assume someone would have asked for this already but I was unable to find any related issues.

